MAPPLET.DESCRIPTION: This mapplet creates 0-n partitions with 0-n subpartitions in the given nm_owner.nm_table using either a highkey_date or a highkey_number. The highkey must be the highest key found in the data to store. Do not add an extra day resp. 1 to it. Subpartitions are added if LIST fields are filled in, otherwise only partitions will be created Return value is always 1 and can be neglected. Mapplet has it's own abort functionality.
MAPPLET.NAME: mpt_create_partitions

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: LIST fields are used for subpartition: in_list_source_table List Source table used in the subpartition template in_list_column Source table column used in the subpartition template in_list_where Where clause condition sentence on Source table used in the subpartition template in_list_source_owner Source table owner (scheme) used in the supartition template
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: in_create_partitions

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: -- Determine GK_DAG of HIGHKEY_DATE if partitioned on date DECODE ( TRUE, -- If partition key is type Month then determine the GK_DAG CD_PARTITION_TYPE = 'M',TO_INTEGER(DATE_DIFF(LAST_DAY(TRUNC(HIGHKEY_DATE, 'DD')), TO_DATE('2000-12-31', 'YYYY-MM-DD'), 'DD')), -- If partition key is not numeric then determine the GK_DAG CD_PARTITION_TYPE <> 'N',TO_INTEGER(DATE_DIFF(TRUNC(HIGHKEY_DATE, 'DD'), TO_DATE('2000-12-31', 'YYYY-MM-DD'), 'DD')), -- Else the key is numeric, use NULL NULL)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: var_HIGHKEY_DATE_GK_DAG

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: -- Determine GK_DAG of HIGHVALUE if partitioned on date DECODE ( TRUE, -- If partition key is on day just use it CD_PARTITION_TYPE = 'D', TO_INTEGER(HIGH_VALUE), -- If partition key is on quarter convert it to day CD_PARTITION_TYPE = 'Q', FLOOR(TO_INTEGER(HIGH_VALUE)/ 100), -- If partition key is on month convert it to day CD_PARTITION_TYPE = 'M', TO_INTEGER(DATE_DIFF(TRUNC(LAST_DAY(TO_DATE(TO_CHAR((TO_INTEGER(HIGH_VALUE) + 200000) * 100 + 1), 'YYYYMMDD')), 'DD'), TO_DATE('2000-12-31', 'YYYY-MM-DD'), 'DD')), NULL)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: var_HIGHVALUE_GK_DAG

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: -- Determine exp_GK_DAG_FROM DECODE ( TRUE, -- If a numeric partition key is used just use the sysdate's GK_DAG CD_PARTITION_TYPE = 'N', TO_INTEGER(DATE_DIFF(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'DD'), TO_DATE('2000-12-31', 'YYYY-MM-DD'), 'DD')), -- If a datebased partition key is used, use next of the current highkey_value CD_PARTITION_TYPE <> 'N', var_HIGHVALUE_GK_DAG + 1 )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: exp_GK_DAG_FROM

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: -- Determine exp_GK_DAG_TO DECODE ( TRUE, -- If a numeric partition key is used and a new partition should be created, the join to the td_dag table has to return 1 records CD_PARTITION_TYPE = 'N' AND HIGHKEY_NUMBER > TO_INTEGER(HIGH_VALUE) - 1, TO_INTEGER(DATE_DIFF(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'DD'), TO_DATE('2000-12-31', 'YYYY-MM-DD'), 'DD')), -- If a numeric partition key is used and a new partition should not be created, the join to the td_dag table has to return 0 records CD_PARTITION_TYPE = 'N' AND HIGHKEY_NUMBER <= TO_INTEGER(HIGH_VALUE) - 1, TO_INTEGER(DATE_DIFF(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'DD'), TO_DATE('2000-12-31', 'YYYY-MM-DD'), 'DD')) - 1, -- If a datebased partition key is used, use the required highkey_date entrie CD_PARTITION_TYPE <> 'N', var_HIGHKEY_DATE_GK_DAG + 1 )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: exp_GK_DAG_TO

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: -- Abort if keys not filled in the right way DECODE ( TRUE, (ISNULL(HIGHKEY_NUMBER) AND CD_PARTITION_TYPE = 'N') OR (ISNULL(HIGHKEY_DATE) AND CD_PARTITION_TYPE <> 'N'), ABORT ( 'High Key is of the wrong type'), 0 )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: exp_ABORT

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: In this expression the specific parameters for the F_PARTITION_CREATE stored procedure are created.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: exp_create_partition_statements

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: -- Create partition name DN_PREFIX_PARTITION || DECODE ( TRUE, CD_PARTITION_TYPE = 'N',TO_CHAR(HIGHKEY_NUMBER), CD_PARTITION_TYPE = 'D',TO_CHAR(ADD_TO_DATE(DT_DATUM,'DD',-1),'YYYYMMDD'), CD_PARTITION_TYPE = 'M',TO_CHAR(ADD_TO_DATE(DT_DATUM,'DD',-1),'YYYYMM'), CD_PARTITION_TYPE = 'Q',TO_CHAR(ADD_TO_DATE(DT_DATUM,'DD',-1),'YYYYMMDD') )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: exp_PARTITION_NAME

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: -- Create partition high_value DECODE ( TRUE, CD_PARTITION_TYPE = 'N',TO_CHAR(HIGHKEY_NUMBER + 1), CD_PARTITION_TYPE = 'D',TO_CHAR(GK_DAG), CD_PARTITION_TYPE = 'M',TO_CHAR(GK_MAAND), CD_PARTITION_TYPE = 'Q',TO_CHAR(GK_KWARTIER) )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: exp_HIGH_VALUE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: -- Create tablespace name DN_PREFIX_TABLESPACE || DECODE ( TRUE, -- Tablespace at year level CD_TABLESPACE_LEVEL = 'Y', TO_CHAR(ADD_TO_DATE(DT_DATUM,'DD',-1),'YYYY'), -- Tablespace at month level CD_TABLESPACE_LEVEL = 'M', TO_CHAR(ADD_TO_DATE(DT_DATUM,'DD',-1),'YYYYMM'), -- Tablespace at day level CD_TABLESPACE_LEVEL = 'D', TO_CHAR(ADD_TO_DATE(DT_DATUM,'DD',-1),'YYYYMMDD'), -- General tablespace CD_TABLESPACE_LEVEL = 'G', '' )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: exp_TABLESPACE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: -- Create indexspace name DN_PREFIX_INDEXSPACE || DECODE ( TRUE, -- Indexspace at year level CD_INDEXSPACE_LEVEL = 'Y', TO_CHAR(ADD_TO_DATE(DT_DATUM,'DD',-1),'YYYY'), -- Indexspace at month level CD_INDEXSPACE_LEVEL = 'M', TO_CHAR(ADD_TO_DATE(DT_DATUM,'DD',-1),'YYYYMM'), -- Indexspace at day level CD_INDEXSPACE_LEVEL = 'D', TO_CHAR(ADD_TO_DATE(DT_DATUM,'DD',-1),'YYYYMMDD'), -- General indexspace CD_INDEXSPACE_LEVEL = 'G', '' )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: exp_INDEXSPACE
